# JPA usage

Queries only in `*Repository` classes. Dynamic filters → Criteria; static → JPQL; native SQL last resort for complex search.

Named parameters always. No `EntityManager` in endpoints.

See [passport-layered-architecture.mdc](passport-layered-architecture.mdc).
